descript.abstract: This data displays the cities of Indonesia. This data was produced by NASA/TRFIC (SEASTAR), but was slightly modified by the World Resources Institute (WRI) by removing Provincial/country capitals from the original data for display purposes for the Interactive Atlas of Indonesia's Forests (2009).
